t-type=image%2Fpng\",\n        \"alt\": \"Luxury modern master bathroom remodel\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"src\": \"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/6982349a56e1e46c7b2e0861/da315904-f176-49cd-9c5f-d3fb752a5853/Essential+White+Bathroom+1.jpg?content-type=image%2Fjpeg\",\n        \"alt\": \"Essential white bathroom remodel\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"src\": \"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/6982349a56e1e46c7b2e0861/31f06899-aa52-4e30-bf5e-0fe5a22dd356/Bathroom1+View2.jpg?content-type=image%2Fjpeg\",\n        \"alt\": \"Modern bathroom remodel view\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"src\": \"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/6982349a56e1e46c7b2e0861/cd44f26c-d314-4820-a9d0-5a698ef24756/Oslo+White+Bathroom-+View+1.jpg?content-type=image%2Fjpeg\",\n        \"alt\": \"Oslo white bathroom remodel\"\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"cta\": {\n    \"heading\": \"Your Dream KitchenIn Just 10 Business Days.\",\n    \"subheading\": \"Expert craftsmanship and guaranteed timelines. Schedule your free consultation to start your transformation.\",\n    \"buttonText\": \"Schedule Free Consultation\",\n    \"bgImage\": \"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/6982349a56e1e46c7b2e0861/1771030625302-7AFG37K0FJK2UDQONSGO/unsplash-image-o-uPDNNSsDA.jpg?format=1500w\"\n  },\n  \"cp\": {\n    \"heading\": \"Recent Projects\",\n    \"projects\": [\n      {\n        \"subtitle\": \"The Modern Forest-Inspired Kitchen\",\n        \"imgSrc\": \"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6982349a56e1e46c7b2e0861/27091dd3-e352-4cf1-b357-54d52fe46556/Photo+May+30+2024%2C+7+52+24+PM.jpg\",\n        \"imgAlt\": \"Modern forest-inspired kitchen remodel in Olympia, Washington — dark cabinetry and wood accents\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"subtitle\": \"University Place Kitchen & Baths\",\n        \"imgSrc\": \"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6982349a56e1e46c7b2e0861/1771537769352-ZB0LBHWMEFZAB4VNPVGU/2.png\",\n        \"imgAlt\": \"University Place kitchen and bath remodel — white shaker cabinets and quartz countertops\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"imgSrc\": \"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6982349a56e1e46c7b2e0861/ee056b21-6388-4643-abb9-f4393ad0dae7/processed-ACF50660-E63C-4936-8770-E221552170B7.jpg\",\n        \"imgAlt\": \"Coastal calm kitchen remodel in Steilacoom, WA — light blue cabinets and white countertops\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"imgSrc\": \"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6982349a56e1e46c7b2e0861/a3efab77-0d76-4d32-8443-6632ed1161a7/1df74c77-21bd-4f67-a624-c083f38633db.png\",\n        \"imgAlt\": \"Heritage woods kitchen remodel in DuPont, WA — wood tone cabinets and natural finishes\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"imgSrc\": \"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6982349a56e1e46c7b2e0861/9812e9cf-a1c7-4380-acee-309e6de86a3e/Photo+Jun+03+2024%2C+10+31+36+AM.jpg\",\n        \"imgAlt\": \"Midnight blue kitchen remodel in South Sound, WA — navy blue cabinetry and gold hardware\"\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"cproc\": {\n    \"heading\": \"Our 5-Step Process\",\n    \"steps\": [\n      {\n        \"text\": \"Vision &Consultation\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"3D Design &Fixed Quote\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"PrecisionPre-Staging\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"The 10-DayBuild\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"FinalWalkthrough\"\n      }\n    ],\n    \"allText\": \"How We Work Our 5-Step Process We respect your time and investment. Our structured approach ensures a stress-free transformation — from the first call to the final walkthrough. 01 Vision &Consultation In-home visit. We listen to your goals and must-haves. 02 3D Design &Fixed Quote Full rendering and binding contract before anything starts. 03 PrecisionPre-Staging Every material ordered and inspected before Day 1. 04 The 10-DayBuild Our crew on site every day. Clean progress, no delays. 05 FinalWalkthrough We don't close until you've approved every detail.\"\n  },\n  \"tst\": {\n    \"heading\": \"Customer Reviews\",\n    \"reviews\": [\n      {},\n      {}\n    ],\n    \"allText\": \"What Clients Say Customer Reviews ★★★★★ Highly Recommended \\\"Highly recommend. Very happy with the outcome of our kitchen. Everyone was professional, friendly and accommodating. Responded immediately to phone calls.\\\" Cathy Sorem ★★★★★ Beyond Expectations \\\"What we really appreciated was how much they genuinely cared. It wasn't just about the job — they checked in, made sure we were comfortable, and seemed invested in our happiness.\\\" Bennett\"\n  },\n  \"ctrans\": {\n    \"heading\": \"Real Transformations\",\n    \"allText\": \"Before & After Real Transformations Drag the slider to reveal BeforeAfterThe 10-Day Black & White Kitchen | Chehalis, WA10 Day Kitchens ← Drag → View Project → BeforeAfterThe Classic Modern Bath | University Place, WA10 Day Kitchens ← Drag → View Project → \\\"Beautiful, functional spaces built around your timeline — completed in 10 business days.\\\" View Full Portfolio\",\n    \"beforeAfters\": [\n      {\n        \"afterSrc\": \"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/6982349a56e1e46c7b2e0861/6c967fbe-1d52-4d18-962b-630ac4d8d319/1c9da333-8da0-44a7-a0b7-ww.jpg\",\n        \"afterAlt\": \"After: The 10-Day Black & White Kitchen in Chehalis, WA\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"afterSrc\": \"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/6982349a56e1e46c7b2e0861/cf0cd942-98d3-4b1c-93e2-663b94a10859/IMG_1165.jpeg\",\n        \"afterAlt\": \"After: The Classic Modern Bath in University Place, WA\"\n      }\n    ],\n    \"beforeImages\": [\n      {\n        \"src\": \"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/6982349a56e1e46c7b2e0861/16eb31c9-48fd-4d06-8aec-6e7190645f80/Photo+Sep+28+2023%2C+12+27+35.jpg\",\n        \"alt\": \"Before: The 10-Day Black & White Kitchen in Chehalis, WA\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"src\": \"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/6982349a56e1e46c7b2e0861/c6840f27-e23f-4686-9aaa-f3a546dc54a7/img00486.jpg\",\n        \"alt\": \"Before: The Classic Modern Bath in University Place, WA\"\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"cc\": {\n    \"heading\": \"Let's Talk AboutYour Project\",\n    \"allText\": \"Contact Let's Talk AboutYour Project Ready to update your space? Reach out today to schedule your free consultation and take the first step toward a kitchen or bathroom designed for real life. Visit Our Showroom 8695 Martin Way E STE 101 Lacey, WA 98516 Call or Text 360-557-3444 Email office@10daykitchens.com Licensed & Insured LIC #10DAYDK757O5 Family Owned 5-Year Warranty Serving Lacey, Olympia, Tacoma, Chehalis and communities throughout Pierce & Thurston Counties. Free Consultation Start Your Project We'll be in touch within 48 hours.\"\n  },\n  \"footer\": {\n    \"allText\": \".fe-698237d601288809eeec4efa { --grid-gutter: calc(var(--sqs-mobile-site-gutter, 6vw) - 11.0px); --cell-max-width: calc( ( var(--sqs-site-max-width, 1500px) - (11.0px * (8 - 1)) ) / 8 ); display: grid; position: relative; grid-area: 1/1/-1/-1; grid-template-rows: repeat(18,minmax(24px, auto)); grid-template-columns: minmax(var(--grid-gutter), 1fr) repeat(8, minmax(0, var(--cell-max-width))) minmax(var(--grid-gutter), 1fr); row-gap: 11.0px; column-gap: 11.0px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-x: clip; } @media (min-width: 768px) { .background-width--inset .fe-698237d601288809eeec4efa { --inset-padd\"\n  }\n}"